{"tid":2511904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度醫院氧氣樽洩漏引火警　至少18人死亡","createTime":"2021-05-01T09:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T09:23:57.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e00d2f6c83d1f0ad1f87213906f9802b4aac65f5","tid":2511904,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"印度醫院氧氣樽洩漏引火警　至少18人死亡<br />\n<br />\n51分鐘前 <br />\n【Now新聞台】印度再有收治新冠病人的醫院失火，至少18人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n事發在西部古吉拉特邦一間醫院的深切治療部，氧氣樽出現洩漏引發火警，消防人員到場救出至少30名病人，至少16名新冠患者和兩名醫護人員喪生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=433203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433203&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=9415860b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433203&h=c59902b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=433203</a>"},{"pid":"2a8b1e8c4524008797d2083e9005f99d526b68d6","tid":2511904,"uid":136797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:18:27.000Z","msg":"係咪用中國製氧氣樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb581b03da2101055e39c72fad84aa8bfe0384ca","tid":2511904,"uid":232228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"點都係要火葬。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3199a2609fb3ab8db0b0a236b86019cc3c1b8ecf","tid":2511904,"uid":61755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb581b03da2101055e39c72fad84aa8bfe0384ca","tid":2511904,"uid":232228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"點都係要火葬。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse